(36, 1342804135, 1342804135, 'How to remove the grease on clothes', '<div align="center"><center><img alt="" src="http://www.nmgnews.com.cn/pic/0/10/08/73/10087377_852250.jpg" /><br /><div align="left">In our life, inevitably clothing glue grease is a plague, then how to handle it?<br />Grease stains-called grease, is a water-soluble stains. Such stains use solvent naphtha, trichlorethylene, tetrachlorethylene, alcohol, acetone, is satisfied that water, bananas, bananas, water, turpentine, benzene and other organic solution, wipe or scrub and other methods to remove grease stains from clothing. Alternatively, you can use some other effective method of removal.<br />1, animal and plant grease removal<br />Animal and plant grease stains in clothing, but also a polar liquid stains. Organic solvents such stains use solvent gasoline, tetrachlorethylene wipe or scrub removal. Stain solution in a timely manner in the scrub to use a towel or cloth to wipe down the drain attached to from the clothing surface. Prevent some stains remain after the solvent to evaporate on the surface of clothing, the clothing will surface traces. If the traces can be repeated wipe or expand the scope scrub to remove. Office of the stains of clothing can also be coated with a water spray in addition to high pressure spray gun.<br />2, the removal of loose grease<br />In the handling of pine, it is easy to make clothing glue pine oil should be promptly removed. According to the principle of pine oil can be dissolved in alcohol, used alcohol or alcohol and turpentine mixture, brushing the stain upon pine grease soaked dissolved, and then a wet towel to wipe adsorption. If you are still traces and then gasoline scrub once rub net repeated several times until clean.<br />3, Tong grease removal<br />Tung oil is a thick vegetable oil, not easy to dry, stick on clothing, difficult to remove. Available gasoline or kerosene, scrub, and tung oil to dissolve and remove, but also with alcohol soap to remove the marks left. Best scouring clothing re-use detergent to clean it again, in order to completely eliminate the traces.<br />4, the removal of the yellow grease<br />The butter is thick animal fat, available toluene or carbon tetrachloride solvent scrubbing, leaving traces of alcohol and ammonia mixture available to remove and can also be used to remove the alcohol soap.<br />5, the curry grease removal<br />Wash away the curry oil stains on clothing are: first with water to the curry grease wetting clothing, and then placed in 50. C temperature and glycerol, scrub, and finally washed with water. If the clothing is cotton, hemp material, available to 10% ammonia solution scrubbing. If clothing is silk, wool material can be used 10% dilute acetic acid wash, and finally with fresh water rinse. Curry oil stains on white clothing, the available concentration of 5% aqueous solution of sodium hypochlorite scrub, then wash with detergent, and finally then rinse clean.<br />6, machine grease removal<br />Available on a lighter machine grease, gasoline scrub, and then clothing and oil pollution at the top and bottom of each pad to a blotting paper or cloth, the iron, so that the further evaporation of oil absorbed by the paper or cloth, so that repeated exchange of paper or cloth ironing repeatedly, until the oil spill all be exhaustion. Finally, washing with detergent, then rinse clean. Darker machine grease, you must use premium gasoline rinse, and then blotting paper or cloth, iron absorption, the last and then rinse with warm water.<br />7, candle grease removal<br />Clothing stained with candle oil, simply relying on the method of washing is not enough. First hand to rub off the wax on the clothing surface, then blotter paper or adsorption pad on the bottom of the stains and then ironing, candles when exposed to heat will melt, melting candle oil absorbed by the paper, such as time to get dirty, it can be repeated several times, candle oil traces will be completely removed.<br />8, chimney grease removal<br />Chimney droplets on clothes, immediately clothes soaked in water to prevent chimney oil and air oxidation. Then crystals of oxalic acid powder sprinkled on the pollution, repeatedly scrub, until the basic addition to the net, and finally to use washing detergent, then rinse clean.<br />9, the coal grease removal<br />Coal oil stains non-polar liquids, dirt, clothing contaminated by kerosene, if not removed will leave a yellow traces, especially the white fabric is more obvious. Removal of coal grease can be used * or magnesium oxide powder to the stain, a few days and then remove the net powder, powder adsorption, coal oil stains will disappear, leaving no trace.<br />10, smoked spots removal<br />Red or purple sweatshirt by smoke, the colors often become gray, and sometimes dark spots, this is because the dye encountered after the carbonic acid gas from the changes. In such cases, as long as alkaline spray again, you can restore the original color.<br />11 cigarettes grease removal<br />Clothing contaminated with amazing cigarette grease, available from 1% to 2% potassium permanganate solution repeatedly scrub, then 3% hydrogen peroxide to repeatedly rub, and finally rinse with water. 12, shoe grease, remove the clothing stained with shoe polish can use the volatile oil wipe, and then the temperature and wash solution to remove the scars. White clothing stained with shoe polish with solvent gasoline wetting then rubbing, and then 10% of the ammonia or ammonia concentrated liquid soap, wash, and finally rinse with warm water to clean.<br />12, asphalt removal of stains<br />Such as wool clothing soiled with asphalt, and are difficult to wash with soap or petrol. Asphalt in the fabric has not yet dry rub in turpentine or benzene solution, then soap scrub, and finally rinse with water. If the asphalt in the fabric to dry, can be used 1:1 turpentine and ether mixture, asphalt dip in the clothing into the mixture soak for 10 minutes, and then squeezed, then removed by rubbing gasoline wipe, wipe after use soap scrub, and finally rinse with water.<br />13, waxed paper correction fluid stains removal<br />Not carefully waxed paper correction fluid dyed clothing, use an alcohol drip stains in clothing at the repeated wipe the final rinse with water stains can be removed to be dry.<br /></div></center></div><br />'),
(37, 1342882470, 1342882470, 'Benefits of swimming', '<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: Simsun; "><img src="http://pic7.nipic.com/20100518/2257382_162839001414_2.jpg" alt="游泳" title="游泳" border="0" height="680" width="482" style="cursor: pointer; " /></span><br /></p><p>Swimming is not only an enhanced physical fitness, strengthen their will, wholesome exercise, and with clinical treatment, the health body will have a significant effect, this drug can not be substituted.<br /><br />Prevention and treatment of obesity<br />Improving the lives of obese elderly are ever more, and the use of slimming teas, medicines, effects and poor, it is recommended that you actively participate in swimming activities, and will obtain the desired results. Swimming is a whole body movement, combined with the friction of water on the surface of the body, can accelerate the systemic capillary blood circulation, enhance metabolism, accelerate the consumption of fat, and the promotion of the limbs, chest and abdomen, back, ministries muscular, enhance internal organs, improve the body resistance to disease, relaxed and happy to achieve harmony and unity of weight loss and bodybuilding.<br /><br />Prevention and treatment of arthritis<br />Including rheumatic, rheumatoid, traumatic, and other types of arthritis are very suitable for swimming, physical therapy. Human joints of arthritis patients in the water swimming, water will produce a mechanical stress, play a good massage to relax stiff joints; the same time, swimming, knee, ankle, etc. do not like running or walking continuous and hard, so that each joint can relax and rest will help the inflammation subsided and functional rehabilitation.<br /><br />Prevention and treatment of asthma<br />Due to the water and the air near the swimming in the water, almost no dust and other substances cause respiratory allergy, it is the most suitable natural environment for people with asthma, in addition to regular swimming exercise can increase lung capacity, respiratory function improve lung, prevention and treatment of asthma is quite beneficial.<br /><br />Prevention varicose veins<br />Swimming because of the lower limb flexion in the water constantly, kicking, or fetch water action, you can increase the tension of the leg muscles, massage, to promote the return of venous blood, eliminate blood stasis swelling vein, which play a treatment or prevention of venous varicose.<br /><br />Prevention and treatment of insomnia or nervous exhaustion<br />Mental, caused inadequate due to Yongnaoguodu physical activity, insomnia or nervous exhaustion by swimming exercise can receive an immediate effect. Swimming is a whole body movement, to accelerate the body renewal, prompting the brain blood circulation, respiratory, digestive and excretory systems and internal organs function improved and improved, in particular, it can adjust the excitation and inhibition of the central nervous system, so as to restore balance, which can quickly insomnia, neurasthenia patients, and better efficacy.<br /></p>');
