(1, 1331820274, 1362259797, 1, 'Order Tutorial', '<p align="left"><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;">Whole shopping process on taobao4us.com</span> </p><p align="left"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;">You are able to&nbsp;shop items from&nbsp;<a style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word;" href="http://www.taobao.com/" target="_blank">www.taobao.com</a></span> through taobao4us.com. </p><p align="left"><strong>1.Register a username&nbsp;on taobao4us.com and login, if you choose products from taobao.com, please copy product link in “Quick Order” text box.</strong></p><p align="left"><img alt="" align="middle" src="/attachments/2012/06/1339169576217509da2d975607.jpg" /><br /></p><p align="left">You will find the product detail page,&nbsp;select size, color, and&nbsp;input quantity. <span style="color:#ff0000;">Note:&nbsp;The selected color will be in&nbsp;grey if it&nbsp;is out of stock.</span></p><p align="left"><img alt="" align="middle" src="/attachments/2012/06/1339170368a9755593eecf69a0.jpg" width="800" /><br /></p><p align="left">Press &quot;Buy Now&quot; to go to shopping cart page, or press &quot;Add to cart&quot; to continue shopping.<br /></p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;On shopping cart page,&nbsp;you can&nbsp;change quantity&nbsp;in your shopping cart. Click &quot;save&quot; to apply your change.&nbsp;</p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><img alt="" align="middle" src="/attachments/2012/06/13391708996997aefc1923a201.jpg" width="800" /><br /></p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left">Click&nbsp;&quot;Generate Order&quot; to generate a new purchase order, and you will be lead to&nbsp;purchase order page.</p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><img alt="" align="middle" src="/attachments/2012/06/13391711976f60276a5baa09a0.jpg" width="800" /><br /></p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left">Your&nbsp;order is on &quot;Unpayed&quot; status.&nbsp;</p><p align="left">Click&nbsp;&quot;View detail&quot; to complete payment with paypal. <span style="color:#ff0000;">Note: Paypal will charge you extra fee of 3.9%+0.3USD.</span></p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><img alt="" align="middle" src="/attachments/2012/06/13391714311a2bf00012a82074.jpg" width="800" /><br /></p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left">Click paypal logo to open payment page. You can use your paypal account balance to pay by login your paypal account.&nbsp;</p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><img alt="" align="middle" src="/attachments/2012/06/1339171842944982a2908cba35.jpg" width="800" /><br /></p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left">If you want to pay with credit card or debit card directly, please click &quot;Create a PayPal account&quot;, and input your card information to complete payment.</p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><img alt="" align="middle" src="/attachments/2012/06/1339172106f88f3d30fe3e2787.jpg" /><br /></p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left">Your purchase order now is on &quot;Payed&quot; status.&nbsp;<br /></p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><img alt="" align="middle" src="/attachments/2012/06/1339172381ad5850067d072043.jpg" /><br /></p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left">Taobao4US&nbsp;will purchase your order within 12 hours and make your order&nbsp;as &quot;Purchased&quot; status.</p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><img alt="" align="middle" src="/attachments/2012/06/1339172536b51c0f4001f144a2.jpg" /><br /></p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left">In about 3 to 5 days, your order will be arrived in taobao4us.com.&nbsp;&nbsp;Your order status will be changed as &quot;Arrived&quot;, and&nbsp;exact weight will be mentioned.</p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><img alt="" align="middle" src="/attachments/2012/06/133917271335e8e28f76bbced3.jpg" /><br /></p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left">When&nbsp;order is arrived, you can&nbsp;go ahead to generate delivery order.</p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left">There are&nbsp;some other status might happen:</p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><span style="color:#ff6666;">Cancelling</span>: Order status will be &quot;Cancelling&quot;&nbsp;when you&nbsp;click cancel before&nbsp;checkout .</p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><span style="color:#ff6666;">Cancelled</span> : order status will be&nbsp;&quot;Cancelled&quot; when your cancel request&nbsp;is approved.</p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><span style="color:#ff6666;">Invalid</span> : Order status will be &quot;Invalid&quot;&nbsp;when your order has been arrived in Taobao4US and not delivered&nbsp;for over 14 days.</p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><span style="color:#ff6666;">Refunded </span>:&nbsp;We will check your parcel before international shipping. Orders will be returned to seller if&nbsp;mismatch&nbsp;happens.&nbsp;All charges will be refunded.</p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><span style="color:#ff6666;">Finished</span> : Order will&nbsp;be &quot;Finished&quot; when your&nbsp;order is&nbsp;delivered.</p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left">&nbsp;</p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left">3. &nbsp; Go to your&nbsp;order list, mark your order and selete your country and express, then press &quot;Delivery&quot; to generate a delivery order.</p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><img alt="" align="middle" src="/attachments/2012/06/1339173707a1b35e05bcc9f63f.jpg" /><br /></p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left">Your delivery order status&nbsp;will be&nbsp;shown as&nbsp;&quot;Unpayed&quot;.</p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><img alt="" align="middle" src="/attachments/2012/06/1339173909ec9295485d75b41e.jpg" /><br /></p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left">Click detail and pay with Paypal, then your delivery order will be in &quot;Payed&quot; status.</p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><img alt="" align="middle" src="/attachments/2012/06/133917401087329b431c62b6c6.jpg" /><br /></p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left">Taobao4US&nbsp;will contact express and input your package tracking number, then&nbsp;your delivery order status will be&nbsp;&quot;Shipped&quot;.</p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><img alt="" align="middle" src="/attachments/2012/06/13391741959fa547bacf2278f4.jpg" /><br /></p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left">You can go to detail page to find your tracking number and check shipping status&nbsp;by express tracking site.</p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><img alt="" align="middle" src="/attachments/2012/06/13391744329100865f4adfc202.jpg" /></p><p><span style="color:#ff0000;">Note:&nbsp;Please&nbsp;check&nbsp;your&nbsp;item''s&nbsp;quantity&nbsp;inside&nbsp;the&nbsp;parcel&nbsp;before&nbsp;you&nbsp;sign,&nbsp;we&nbsp;are&nbsp;not&nbsp;responsible&nbsp;for&nbsp;the&nbsp;loss&nbsp;once&nbsp;you&nbsp;sign&nbsp;the&nbsp;consignment&nbsp;note.&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;</p><p>If you find any missing items, please write down the&nbsp;product detail and missing quantity&nbsp;on your consignment note and give back to the courier. </p><p>Then email to <a href="mailto:taobao4us@hotmail.com">taobao4us@hotmail.com</a> the photo of the parcel with the weight show together.</p><p>We will verify with our shipping agent in China&nbsp;and will get back to you after we get reply.</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left">4. Click &quot;Confirm&quot; and leave your testimonial when you receive your order.</p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><img alt="" align="middle" src="/attachments/2012/06/13391748838aa27b0c480aa8b8.jpg" /><br /></p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><img alt="" align="middle" src="/attachments/2012/06/133917494911e3c43341032138.jpg" /><br /></p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left">Your delivered order will be&nbsp;shown as &quot;Finished&quot;.</p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><img alt="" align="middle" src="/attachments/2012/06/1339175128ad2aef1c77390ea5.jpg" /><br /></p><p>There&nbsp;are&nbsp;also&nbsp;some&nbsp;other&nbsp;status&nbsp;below&nbsp;maybe&nbsp;happened:</p><p><span style="color:#ff6666;">Cancelling</span>: Order status will be &quot;Cancelling&quot; when you click cancel before checkout .</p><p>Cancelled: Order status will be &quot;Cancelled&quot; when your cancel request is approved.</p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left">&nbsp;</p><p><span style="color:#cccccc;"></span>&nbsp;</p><p><span style="color:#cccccc;">Tags：whole shopping process , how to buy from taobao4us.com</span></p><br />', '1', '', 'order-tutorial'),
(2, 1338546278, 1362178311, 1, 'Registration & Setting', '<p><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;"><strong>How to&nbsp;become Taobao4US member?</strong></span></p><p><span style="font-family:Arial;">Please click “Register” on the top left of taobao4us.com</span><span style="font-family:Arial;">. Enter required information and click “Register”. A verification letter will be sent to your registered email, please click the link in your letter to activate your account.&nbsp;</span></p><p><br /></p><p><strong><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;">How to activate my account?</span></strong></p><p>When&nbsp;submit your user information, you should receive an activation email. Click the link in the email to activate your account. If youdidn''t receive an e-mail, it can be caused by the following:</p><p>1)Please confirm you have input your email correctly.</p><p>2)Please check your email spam folder.</p><p>3)Please reregister with another email address if&nbsp;the email is rejected by your email provider.</p><p>4)Please use another email address if&nbsp;you registered with Facebook Email.</p><p>5)Please send an email to <a href="mailto:taobao4us@hotmail.com">taobao4us@hotmail.com</a> by using the email registered. And we will manually activate for you.&nbsp;</p><p><br /></p><p><strong><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;">Can I change my Email address and username? </span></strong></p><p>Email and username cannot be changed as soon as you registered. Please input them carefully before you register.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;">What should I do if I forget my password? </span></strong></p><p>You can create a new password by clicking &quot;Lost&nbsp;passward? &quot; in login page.&nbsp;You will receive a email to reset your password.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;">How to change my password? </span></strong></p><p>After you log in, please go to “My Account” - &quot;Account Info&quot; page to reset your password.</p><p><br /></p><p><span style="color:#cccccc;"><strong>Tags</strong>：taobaoenglishagent'' registration, activate account, how to join taobaoenglishagent.com.&nbsp;</span></p>', '1', '', 'registration-and-setting'),
(3, 1338546308, 1362173152, 1, 'About Taobao4US', '<p>Taobao4US&nbsp;is the most professional and reliable shopping agency in United States. We serve a wide range of clients from Multi-national corporation to individuals worldwide. For companies and individuals who wish to shop online in China, <a href="http://www.taobao4us.com">www.taobao4us.com</a> is your trustful and private partner.&nbsp;</p><p><br /></p><p>Our mission is to assist and help all the friends outside of China to safely purchase items from&nbsp;Chinese online stores. We&nbsp;collabrate with the largest Chinese&nbsp;online store,&nbsp;<a href="http://www.taobao.com/">www.taobao.com</a>.&nbsp;Anyone who would like to shop&nbsp;from&nbsp;Chinese online stores&nbsp;can benefit from our service. Most online stores are displayed in Chinese, so we will assist and help our buyers to find out what the stores are offering, the prices, and also advise you hot deals. &nbsp;It is our duty to make our services available for everyone by providing a safe payment method and cheap, fast, and reliable shipping.&nbsp;</p><p><br /></p><p>We are a professional purchasing agency ready to assist you in purchasing any item in China. For your benefit, satisfaction and convenience, we will assist you by providing the best value&nbsp;to save&nbsp;your time and money. Join us today and enjoy your China shopping right way. &nbsp;</p><p><br /></p><p>Our mission: <span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';color:#cc0000;">Easy, safe and&nbsp;economy shopping!</span></p>', '1', 'http://www.taobaoenglishagent.com/guide/view/about-taobaoenglishagent.html', 'About taobao4us .com'),
(4, 1338546333, 1342590460, 1, 'Customer Instruction', '<span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;">&nbsp;<strong>1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Fees:</strong></span> <p align="left">&nbsp;1) Domestic shipping fee: If you buy multiple items from the same seller, you will&nbsp; save much on domestic shipping. </p><p align="left"><span style="color:#ff6666;">Note:&nbsp; If the domestic shipping fee is not retrieved, we will charge you 12CNY shipping fee.</span> </p><p align="left">2) taobaoenglishagent Service Fee: 10% of items fee + shipping costs. Our minimum service fee is 5USD per parcel. taobaoenglishagent will still charge you 5USD even if (item fee + domestic shipping) is less than 5USD. </p><p align="left">3) Handling charges for different payment methods:&nbsp;</p><div align="center"><table border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="18%"><tbody><tr><td valign="top"><p align="center"><strong>PayPal</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td valign="top"><p align="center">Only accepts US Dollars</p></td></tr><tr><td valign="top"><p align="center">3.9%+0.3USD</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p align="left">﹡:&nbsp;<span style="text-align: -webkit-center; ">3.9%+0.3USD</span> means the bank will charge that, taobaoenglishagent.com won''t charge you any bank service fee. </p><p align="left">4) Freight charges: </p><table border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tbody><tr><td valign="top"><p align="center"><strong>Express vendors</strong></p></td><td valign="top"><p align="center"><strong>EMS</strong></p></td><td valign="top"><p align="center"><strong>China Post</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td valign="top"><p align="center"><strong>Discount</strong></p></td><td valign="top"><p align="center">50% off</p></td><td valign="top"><p align="center">NONE </p></td></tr></tbody></table><p align="left">5) Exchange Rate: Based on the exchange rate announced by the Bank of China, Our exchange rate currently: 1CNY=0.16USD. </p><p align="left"><br /></p><p align="left"><strong><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Time: </span></strong></p><p align="left">1)&nbsp; Arrival of goods to taobaoenglishagent: Usually takes 3-5 days after we purchased. </p><p align="left">2)&nbsp; Shipping date: After you submitted delivery and paid&nbsp; for it. </p><p align="left">3)&nbsp; International delivery time: Normally, EMS takes 7-15 days, Air parcel 15-35 days. </p><p align="left"><br /></p><p align="left"><strong><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Service: </span></strong></p><p align="left">1)&nbsp; Our minimum service fee is 5USD, but there is no minimum order requirement. </p><p align="left">2) &nbsp;Virtual goods: We do not accept this kind purchase, which includes gift cards, game tokens, etc. due to illegal practices. </p><p align="left">3) &nbsp;Quality of goods: We will verify size, quantity, colour, pattern of the goods, but we are not responsible for quality. </p><p align="left">4) &nbsp;Electronic products: We can only verify the appearance and model. </p><p align="left"><br /></p><p align="left"><strong><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Customs: </span></strong></p><p align="left">1) We guarantee clearance at Chinese customs, and we will bear responsibility for all problems associated with Chinese customs. </p><p align="left">2)&nbsp; Destination customs: If there are tariff requirements or confiscated goods in your country, we cannot be responsible for damage or loss. </p><p align="left"><span style="color:#cccccc;"><strong>Tags</strong>：general information, customer guide, purchasing guide </span></p>', '1', '', 'customer-instruction'),
(6, 1338546394, 1362174453, 2, 'Delivery Methods', '<strong><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;">What international shipping methods are available in Taobao4US ? </span></strong><p>Taobao4US&nbsp;provides various kinds of shipping methods: </p><p><strong>EMS /&nbsp;China Post: Air parcel, SAL parcel /&nbsp;UPS /&nbsp;DHL /&nbsp;TNT</strong></p><p><strong><br /></strong></p><p><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;">EMS </span></p><p>EMS express company: Packages will arrive to destination within 5 - 7 days. Services will be slower during busy season, reaching up to 10-22 Days. </p><p>Three days after item has mailed out, the status of the parcel will appear and will be constantly updated on the EMS website. If you have not received the packages after 12 days, please track the information on your own country’s postal website or contact your local post office. </p><p>Note: It is unsafe to ship items to Spain by EMS,&nbsp; if the weight of parcel is over 7 kilograms. As the custom is very strict about&nbsp; parcel weight, we suggest you should ship them by dividing into several parcels and during this time, our delivery speed may slow down.Hope you can understand that. </p><p><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;">China Post (Airmail, SAL)</span></p><p>International package includes Air parcel and SAL parcel, and their prices is lower compared to EMS. With Air parcel, item will reach destination within 10 - 20 days. However, it may takes up to 30 days during busy season. If the package did not arrive after a month, please visit your country’s tracking website for more information. Chinese tracking site is updated according to the feedback from your country, so tracking from your country''s site will be more prompt and accurate. </p><p>International air parcel (for goods less than 2kg): items will reach destination in 20 - 30 days. Tracking works the same way as that of international packages. </p><p><br /></p><p><strong><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;">When will I get the parcel after the&nbsp;ship date? </span></strong></p><table border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tbody><tr><td valign="top"><p>Delivery Method </p></td><td valign="top"><p>ETA </p></td></tr><tr><td valign="top"><p>EMS </p></td><td valign="top"><p>In 7-22 days </p></td></tr><tr><td valign="top"><p>Air parcel </p></td><td valign="top"><p>In 15-30 days </p></td></tr><tr><td valign="top"><p>SAL parcel </p></td><td valign="top"><p>In 15-30 days </p></td></tr><tr><td valign="top"><p>UPS/DHL/TNT/FedEx</p></td><td valign="top"><p>In&nbsp;3-5 days </p></td></tr></tbody></table><p><strong><br /></strong></p><p><strong><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;">Customs</span></strong> </p><p>You can refer to the following suggestions: </p><p>1, weight of the package<em><strong>:</strong></em> </p><p>In many countries, a parcel will be considered commercial if it weights over 10kg. Customs will block these parcels and you will be required to pay duties. To prevent this, you should monitor the weight of your parcel. </p><p>2, items in package<em><strong>:</strong></em> </p><p>Having too many similar items in the same parcel will draw&nbsp; Customs’&nbsp; much attention. You should not send large numbers of similar products together. Instead, separate them into different parcels. </p><p>Advice: </p><p>1) Japan Customs are very strict. Do not try to deliver counterfeit to Japan. 80% of them will be confiscated by Japan Customs. </p><p>2) Italy Customs will pay special attention to counterfeit shoes. Compared to other European countries, Italy customs are the strictest. </p>', '1', '', 'delivery-methods');
