T: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 20px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; FONT: 12px/22px Arial; WHITE-SPACE: normal; ORPHANS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 10px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" class="ulitem_img"><p style="COLOR: rgb(16,16,16)">These delivery way are very fast (3-5days) and the service is very good. They are suitable for the heavy products. If the products'' weight is above 20kg, the cost will be lower than EMS. If the products'' weight is below 20kg, the cost is expensive although taobaoenglishagent can cut your&nbsp;Fuel from. Thees 3 express companies can''t deliver liquid, powder and copy-brand products. The delivery status can also be checked online according to the tracking number.</p><p style="COLOR: rgb(16,16,16)">Go to <a href="http://www.yw56.com.cn/english/diy8.asp">http://www.yw56.com.cn/english/diy8.asp</a>&nbsp;to check prices.</p><p><span style="font-size:18px;color:#ff0000;"><strong>We will not charge you&nbsp;fuel surcharge which means another 30%off !</strong></span></p><span style="color:#101010;">* Sometimes the freight will be charged according to dimensional weight which is a calculation of a theoretical weight of a package. If you ship some low density packages, please be careful, it may be charged according to the dimensional weight. Calculation method: (L cm x W cm x H cm)/5000</span></ul><p>&nbsp;</p>', '1', '', 'shipping-price');
