target="_blank">Taiwan</a> <a href="http://www.posta.co.tz/tracking.htm" target="_blank">Tanzania</a> <a href="http://www.poste.tn/" target="_blank">Tunisia</a> </p><p>U: <a href="https://www.royalmail.com/portal/sme/trackresult" target="_blank">Kingdom</a> <a href="http://www.correo.com.uy/index.asp?codPag=tyt" target="_blank">Uruguay</a> <a href="http://www.ukrposhta.com/www/upost_en.nsf/search_post?openpage" target="_blank">Ukraine</a> </p><p>V: <a href="http://www.postvanuatu.com/" target="_blank">Vanuatu</a> </p><p>Note:You can click your country name when the parcel has arrived in your country , and then check the parcel status. </p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;">What should I do if I can''t track my parcel?</span></strong> </p><p>If you come across this problem, please verify the following: </p><p>● &nbsp; Did you enter the right tracking number? </p><p>● &nbsp; Did you choose the right tracking website? </p><p>If you answered yes, then contact our customer service to check for you.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;">Why i can''t find information about my parcel?</span></strong> </p><p>1. Most of the time, it''s because the information has not been updated by the shipping company. </p><p>China Post (EMS, Airmail, SAL) </p><p>a) &nbsp; &nbsp; Sometimes tracking information will not be updated in time. They need at least 3 days for tracking to be posted. Please be patient. </p><p>b) &nbsp; &nbsp;If the parcel was sent during public holidays, the information may be available after the holiday. </p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;">Why my parcel status did not change?</span></strong> </p><p>When your package leaves Beijing, it will be put in queue to be delivered to your country. During this transit, the status will not change, so it is common to see your package stuck in the status &quot;Dispatch ...&quot; This transit is the longest process, and usually takes 7-10 days (or up to 30 days during busy seasons) </p><p><strong></strong>&nbsp;</p><p><strong><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;">When is the busy season?</span></strong> </p><p>Busy season is November to February every year. This is because of Christmas and Chinese New Year. </p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;">What should I do if I did not get the parcel after a long time?</span></strong> </p><p>If you still do not get your parcel 30 days after the shipping date, please contact us for help tracking your parcel. taobaoenglishagent will request China Post Office to provide us with the tracking list of the parcel. Please email us the following information: </p><p>* Tracking number. </p><p>* The complete information as listed below: </p><p>Name: </p><p>Address: </p><p>City: </p><p>Country: </p><p>Post Code: </p><p>Telephone: </p><p>The above information should be identical to the one on the waybill. </p><p>It might take a long time to get the detailed tracking list. Generally speaking, initial checking will take one week. Sometimes the tracking might fail, and the China Post Office will have to send the request again. </p><p>If there is no confirmation from China Post Office before deadline, we will treat the parcel as lost and you will get compensation according to our Insurance Policy. </p><p>Confirmation deadline after shipping date* </p><p>(Please note that the shipping date and final delivery date are subject to the exact date on the tracking website.) </p><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tbody><tr><td valign="top"><p>Shipping Methods </p></td><td valign="top"><p>EMS </p></td><td valign="top"><p>Airmail </p></td><td valign="top"><p>SAL parcel </p></td></tr><tr><td valign="top"><p>Deadline </p></td><td valign="top"><p>60 days </p></td><td valign="top"><p>75 days </p></td><td valign="top"><p>90 days </p></td></tr></tbody></table><p><strong></strong>&nbsp;</p><p><strong><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;">If my parcel lost, can I get compensation?</span></strong> </p><p>For the insured parcel, taobaoenglishagent will give you full compensation if the parcel lost during the delivery; for the uninsured parcel, taobaoenglishagent can only shoulder the international shipping fee for you. So we strongly recommend you to choose insurance for your parcel. </p>', '1', '', 'delivery-tracking'),
(9, 1338546505, 1342591090, 2, 'Customs', '<strong><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;">What should I know about customs?</span></strong> <p align="left">In order to protect the interests of our customers, taobaoenglishagent will handle the parcels according to each country''s regulations to avoid taxes. </p><p align="left">taobaoenglishagent will assure that the goods clear China Customs, but we can not be responsible for clearance in your country. </p><p align="left">If your shipment has been held by customs, you might need to pay taxes to get your parcel. This is unlikely, only 0.3% of the parcels we delivery have been taxed. </p><p align="left">We suggest that before shipping,taobaoenglishagent customers take the initiative to find out policies of their local customs. In countries with high rate of customs clearance, there is no need to pay any fees. However, in countries with low rate of customs clearance such as Argentina, customers may be required to pay tariffs. </p><p align="left"><br /></p><p align="left"><strong><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;">How to avoid? </span></strong></p><p align="left">You can refer to the following suggestions: </p><p align="left">1, weight of the package: </p><p align="left">In many countries, a parcel will be considered commercial if it weights over 10kg. Customs will block these parcels and ask you to pay duties. To prevent this, you should monitor the weight of your parcel. </p><p align="left">2, items in package: </p><p align="left">Having too many similar items in the same parcel will draw the Customs'' attention. You should not send large numbers of similar products together. Instead, separate them into different parcels. </p><p align="left"><br /></p><p align="left"><strong><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;">Some advices:</span></strong> </p><p align="left">1) Japanese Customs are very strict. Do not try to deliver counterfeit items to Japan. 80% of parcels will be confiscated by Japan Customs. </p><p align="left">2) Italian Customs will pay special attention to counterfeit shoes. Compared to other European countries, Italian customs are the strictest. </p><p align="left"><span style="color:#cccccc;">Tags：how to avoid tax, customs clearance </span></p>', '1', '', 'customs'),
(10, 1338546536, 1342591143, 3, 'Pay with Paypal', '<p></p><p align="left" style="font-weight: bold; ">Press paypal logo to open payment page. If you want to use your paypal account balance, please login and pay.&nbsp;</p><p align="left" style="font-weight: bold; "><img src="http://www.taobaoenglishagent.com/attachments/2012/06/1339171842944982a2908cba35.jpg" align="middle" alt="" width="800" /><br /></p><p align="left" style="font-weight: bold; ">If you want to pay with credit card or debit card directly, please press &quot;Create a PayPal account&quot;, and input your card information to complete payment.</p><p align="left" style="font-weight: bold; "><img src="http://www.taobaoenglishagent.com/attachments/2012/06/1339172106f88f3d30fe3e2787.jpg" align="middle" alt="" /></p><br /><p><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0); ">Note: Paypal will charge you extra fee of 3.9%+0.3USD.</span><br /></p>', '1', '', 'pay-with-paypal'),
(11, 1338546556, 1362260137, 3, 'Charge Policy', '<span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;">Taobao4US'' total fee = First payment + Second payment</span><p align="left"><strong>First payment: &nbsp;</strong>Items'' fee + China domestic shipping fee</p><p align="left"><strong>Second payment: </strong>International&nbsp;shipping fee + Service fee + Customs fee</p><p align="left">Taobao4US''&nbsp;payment methods : PayPal</p><p align="left"><br /></p><p align="left"><strong><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Service fee:</span></strong></p><p align="left">Taobao4US'' service fee = (Items fee + domestic shipping fee) X <span style="font-size:24px;"><span style="color:#ff0000;">6</span><strong><span style="color:#ff0000;">%</span></strong></span></p><p align="left">SVIP member will enjoy service fee&nbsp;as low as <span style="font-size:24px;color:#ff0000;">5%</span>.</p><p align="left">The minimum service charge is 5.0 USD per parcel. </p><p align="left">For example:<br />If the items costs 100USD and domestic shipping is 6USD,&nbsp;Taobao4US will charge you 6.36 USD service fee.<br />(100+6)×0.06 = 6.36USD<br /><br />If the items costs 10USD, and domestic shipping is 3.6USD,&nbsp;Taobao4US will charge you 5USD.<br />(10+3.6)×0.06 =&nbsp; 0.816USD ＜5USD<br /><br />Note:Taobao4US storage time limit is 180 days, and during this time, your order status is &quot;Arrived&quot;; we won''t help you to store if the date is more than 180 days and then your order status will change to &quot;Invalid&quot;. &quot;Invalid&quot; means that your''ve given up your items and we will handle them in our way. </p><p align="left"><br /></p><p align="left"><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>Items fee:</strong></span> </p><p align="left">The item price is as&nbsp;shown on the shopping site you browsing. </p><p align="left"><br /></p><p align="left"><strong><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Domestic shipping fee: </span></strong></p><p align="left">Most domestic delivery companies charge 12 to 30 CNY per kilogram. The fee differs according to the courier, parcel weight and the distance between seller and buyer''s locations.&nbsp;</p><p align="left">For the items from same seller, if the total weight from this seller is below 1kg, we will charge you one time. If above 1kg, you need to pay the&nbsp;balance.</p><p align="left"><br /></p><p align="left"><strong><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; International delivery fee: </span></strong></p><p align="left">Taobao4US provide various delivery methods, such as: EMS, Airmail for small packages, Air Parcel, SAL Parcel, Domestic forwarding. &nbsp;</p><p align="left"><br /></p><p align="left"><strong>5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Customs fee: </strong></p><p align="left">We suggest that before shipping, Taobao4US customers take the initiative to find out policies of their local customs. In countries with high rate of customs clearance, there is no need to pay any fees. However, in countries with low rate of customs clearance such as Argentina, customers may be required to pay tariffs. </p><p align="left">Note: Chinese customs fee is <span>(Items fee + domestic shipping fee)*1%</span>. </p><p align="left"><br /></p><p align="left"><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;">When to pay the service fee?</span></span></p><p align="left">You will be asked to pay service charge together with the international shipping&nbsp;fee for your parcel. After you get the weight of your parcel and have selected the international shipping method, Taobao4US will automatically calculate the service fee for you. At that point, you will need to pay the shipping costs and service fee, and Taobao4US will ship your parcel.<br /><br /></p>', '1', '', 'charge-policy'),
(12, 1338546587, 1362177169, 3, 'points and promotion', '<strong><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;">How can I get points?</span></strong><p>1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; You will get 100 points when you register on taobao4us.com.</p><p>2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;You will get same points as the amount of your orders when you&nbsp;shop on taobao4us.com. For example,&nbsp;you will get 50 points when&nbsp;your purchase order is $50.</p><p>3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; When you are apply to be a points-back promoter, then you will get same points as the money of your direct referral’s orders. For example, if one of your direct referrals consumed $50, then you will get 50 points.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;">How can I get discount?</span></strong></p><p>1. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; All discount is for your serivce fee.</p><p>2. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; When you register in taobao4us.com with a inviter user name, you&nbsp;will have 20% discount service fee for your first delivery.</p><p>3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;A member lever rules is shown as below.&nbsp;&nbsp;You will have relavant discount when you reach the point level.</p><div align="center"><table border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tbody><tr><td valign="top"><p align="center">Level</p></td><td valign="top"><p align="center">Point from</p></td><td valign="top"><p align="center">Point to</p></td><td valign="top"><p align="center">Discount</p></td></tr><tr><td valign="top"><p align="center">Member</p></td><td valign="top"><p align="center">0</p></td><td valign="top"><p align="center">999</p></td><td valign="top"><p align="center">0%</p></td></tr><tr><td valign="top"><p align="center">VIP</p></td><td valign="top"><p align="center">1000</p></td><td valign="top"><p align="center">9999</p></td><td valign="top"><p align="center">10%</p></td></tr><tr><td valign="top"><p align="center">SVIP</p></td><td valign="top"><p align="center">10000</p></td><td valign="top"><p align="center">99999</p></td><td valign="top"><p align="center">20%</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong><br /></strong></p><p><strong><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;">What&nbsp;will I be&nbsp;rewarded i<strong><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;">f I am a promoter</span></strong>?</span></strong></p><p>1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; If you are a point-back promoter, you will get same points as the money of your direct referral’s orders. For example, if one of your direct referrals consumed $50, then you will get 50 points.</p><p>2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; If you are a cache-back promoter, you will get 30% service fee of your direct referrals. For example, if one of your direct referrals consumed $50, then the service fee is $5, you will get $1.5. The more your direct referrals, the more cache-back you will earn.</p>', '1', '', 'points-and-promotion'),
(13, 1338546629, 1362260817, 4, 'Shopping Tips', '<p><strong><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:24px;color:#cc0000;">How&nbsp;to find&nbsp;an item on Taobao.com?</span></strong></p><p>Clothing </p><p>For example, </p><p>Iif you are looking for men''s G-star''s jeans, you would enter&quot; G-star 牛仔裤 男&quot; in the TaoBao search bar.</p><p>If you are looking for men''s POLO T-shirt, you would enter&quot; POLO 男 T恤&quot;. </p><p>Generally, you can search with English or simply use the format: Brand + type + sex! </p><p>Here are some words that you may use: </p><p>English&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Chinese </p><p>man&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 男 </p><p>woman &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;女 </p><p>bag&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 包 </p><p>jeans &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 牛仔裤 </p><p>suit&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 西装 </p><p>coat&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 外套 </p><p>shoes&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 鞋子 </p><p>T-shirt&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; T恤 </p><p>jacket &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 夹克 </p><p>shoes &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;鞋 </p><p>skirt &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 裙 </p><p>More... </p><p>Electronic device </p><p>You can enter the product code in the search bar. </p><p>For example, if you are looking for Nokia N97, </p><p>you can enter “Nokia N97” or “诺基亚 N97” </p><p>If you are looking for Joyoung soymilk maker which has product ID JYDZ-17A, </p><p>you simply enter “JYDZ-17A”. </p><p>If you still need help finding your goods, please contact Taobao4US Customer Service. </p><p><br /></p><p><strong><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;"><span style="color:#cc0000;">How&nbsp;to view the seller’s reputation? </span></span></strong></p><p>Just under the seller’s name, you can see heart(s)/diamond(s)/crown(s) which represents how many points the seller has (seller gets 1 point for each positive rating, and -1 for each negative rating). &nbsp;Next to that, you can see the shop’s “positive rating” (好评率) which is rated by the buyers who have bought from this seller. The best performance is 好评率：100%. </p><p>&nbsp;</p><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tbody><tr><td valign="top"><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Red heart(s): 4 – 250 points </p><p>Blue diamond(s): 251 – 10000 points </p><p>Blue crown(s):10001 – 500000 points </p><p>Golden crown(s): more than 500000 points </p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Note: </p><p>Every positive rating gives the seller 1 point. </p><p>Every negative rating takes away 1 point. </p></td></tr></tbody></table><p><strong><br /></strong></p><p><strong><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';font-size:18px;"><span style="color:#cc0000;">What are TaoBao domestic delivery options? </span></span></strong></p><p>There are three methods of Domestic Delivery in China: Surface Mail (平邮), Express Delivery (快递) and EMS. </p><p>taobaoenglishagent does not accept Surface Mail because of the following reasons: </p><p>1. It’s slow. It will take at least 7 days. </p><p>2. It’s dangerous. Goods has a higher chance of being lost or damaged. </p><p>3. Most importantly, the goods will not reach our company directly! It requires recipient to personally pick up the item from the Post Office. </p><p>taobaoenglishagent recommends Express Delivery! Express Delivery is reliable and we will receive the items 3-7 days after item has been shipped. </p><p>If you are in a hurry or&nbsp; items are expensive, EMS might be a better option. EMS is more costly but with&nbsp; the most reliable service and the goods will reach to us within 1-2 days after being shipped. </p><p><span style="color:#cccccc;">Tags：search tips, shopping guide, shopping tips </span></p>', '1', '', 'shopping-tips'),
(14, 1338546658, 1362260758, 4, 'Purchasing Notice', '<p><strong><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;">Besides taobao.com, can we purchase from other websites? </span></strong></p><p>We recommend <a href="http://www.taobao.com/">www.taobao.com</a> which is the biggest shopping platform in China. If you cannot find what you need there, we can&nbsp;help you buy from <a href="http://www.paipai.com/">www.paipai.com</a>, <a href="http://www.eachnet.com/">www.eachnet.com</a>, <a href="http://www.dangdang.com/">www.dangdang.com</a>, <a href="http://www.amazon.cn/">www.amazon.cn</a> etc. </p><p>Please contact our customer service if you are interested in other Chines online stores.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;. </p><p><br /></p><p><strong><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;">What kind of&nbsp;products&nbsp;cannot&nbsp;be purchased? </span></strong></p><p>We can''t purchase animals, plants, large-sized cargos, virtual items, heavy metal raw material, toxic or radioactive heavy metal products,and items beyond our purchasing ability and other illegal products. Besides, we reserve the right to reject some illegal and unreasonable requests. </p><p><br /></p><p><strong><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;">What will we&nbsp;do when&nbsp;your order arrive? </span></strong></p><p>For clothing and accessories, we will check size, color, quantity and pattern. For electronic products, we can do some very basic checking, like whether the appearance is in good condition or not, whether it can be powered on and off. We cannot make sure that the inside parts or the software are the same, you are at your own risk. </p><p><br /></p><p><strong><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;">Why the&nbsp;stock information sometimes not true? </span></strong></p><p>The stock information on Taobao webpage is not updated in time.<br />This is the reason why sometimes you''ll get feedback that the goods are out of stock although the webpage shows they are available. </p><p><span style="color:#cccccc;">Tags：purchasing policy, purchasing notice </span></p>', '1', '', 'purchasing-notice'),
(33, 1362266603, 1362266786, 1, 'Order Tutorial & Charge Policy', '<p align="left"><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:32px;color:#666666;"><strong>Order Tutorial</strong></span></p><p align="left"><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;">Whole shopping process on taobao4us.com</span> </p><p align="left"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;">You are able to shop items from <a style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); word-wrap: break-word;" href="http://www.taobao.com/" target="_blank">www.taobao.com</a></span> through taobao4us.com. </p><p align="left"><strong>1.Register a username on taobao4us.com and login, if you choose products from taobao.com, please copy product link in “Quick Order” text box.</strong></p><p align="left"><img alt="" align="middle" src="/attachments/2012/06/1339169576217509da2d975607.jpg" /><br /></p><p align="left">You will find the product detail page, select size, color, and input quantity. <span style="color:#ff0000;">Note: The selected color will be in grey if it is out of stock.</span></p><p align="left"><img alt="" align="middle" src="/attachments/2012/06/1339170368a9755593eecf69a0.jpg" width="800" /><br /></p><p align="left">Press &quot;Buy Now&quot; to go to shopping cart page, or press &quot;Add to cart&quot; to continue shopping.<br /></p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left">2.&nbsp;&nbsp; On shopping cart page, you can change quantity in your shopping cart. Click &quot;save&quot; to apply your change. </p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><img alt="" align="middle" src="/attachments/2012/06/13391708996997aefc1923a201.jpg" width="800" /><br /></p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left">Click &quot;Generate Order&quot; to generate a new purchase order, and you will be lead to purchase order page.</p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><img alt="" align="middle" src="/attachments/2012/06/13391711976f60276a5baa09a0.jpg" width="800" /><br /></p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left">Your order is on &quot;Unpayed&quot; status. </p><p align="left">Click &quot;View detail&quot; to complete payment with paypal. <span style="color:#ff0000;">Note: Paypal will charge you extra fee of 3.9%+0.3USD.</span></p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><img alt="" align="middle" src="/attachments/2012/06/13391714311a2bf00012a82074.jpg" width="800" /><br /></p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left">Click paypal logo to open payment page. You can use your paypal account balance to pay by login your paypal account. </p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><img alt="" align="middle" src="/attachments/2012/06/1339171842944982a2908cba35.jpg" width="800" /><br /></p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left">If you want to pay with credit card or debit card directly, please click &quot;Create a PayPal account&quot;, and input your card information to complete payment.</p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><img alt="" align="middle" src="/attachments/2012/06/1339172106f88f3d30fe3e2787.jpg" /><br /></p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left">Your purchase order now is on &quot;Payed&quot; status. <br /></p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><img alt="" align="middle" src="/attachments/2012/06/1339172381ad5850067d072043.jpg" /><br /></p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left">Taobao4US will purchase your order within 12 hours and make your order as &quot;Purchased&quot; status.</p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><img alt="" align="middle" src="/attachments/2012/06/1339172536b51c0f4001f144a2.jpg" /><br /></p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left">In about 3 to 5 days, your order will be arrived in taobao4us.com.&nbsp; Your order status will be changed as &quot;Arrived&quot;, and exact weight will be mentioned.</p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><img alt="" align="middle" src="/attachments/2012/06/133917271335e8e28f76bbced3.jpg" /><br /></p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left">When order is arrived, you can go ahead to generate delivery order.</p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left">There are some other status might happen:</p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><span style="color:#ff6666;">Cancelling</span>: Order status will be &quot;Cancelling&quot; when you click cancel before checkout .</p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><span style="color:#ff6666;">Cancelled</span> : order status will be &quot;Cancelled&quot; when your cancel request is approved.</p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><span style="color:#ff6666;">Invalid</span> : Order status will be &quot;Invalid&quot; when your order has been arrived in Taobao4US and not delivered for over 14 days.</p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><span style="color:#ff6666;">Refunded </span>: We will check your parcel before international shipping. Orders will be returned to seller if mismatch happens. All charges will be refunded.</p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><span style="color:#ff6666;">Finished</span> : Order will be &quot;Finished&quot; when your order is delivered.</p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"> </p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left">3.&nbsp;&nbsp; Go to your order list, mark your order and selete your country and express, then press &quot;Delivery&quot; to generate a delivery order.</p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><img alt="" align="middle" src="/attachments/2012/06/1339173707a1b35e05bcc9f63f.jpg" /><br /></p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left">Your delivery order status will be shown as &quot;Unpayed&quot;.</p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><img alt="" align="middle" src="/attachments/2012/06/1339173909ec9295485d75b41e.jpg" /><br /></p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left">Click detail and pay with Paypal, then your delivery order will be in &quot;Payed&quot; status.</p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><img alt="" align="middle" src="/attachments/2012/06/133917401087329b431c62b6c6.jpg" /><br /></p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left">Taobao4US will contact express and input your package tracking number, then your delivery order status will be &quot;Shipped&quot;.</p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><img alt="" align="middle" src="/attachments/2012/06/13391741959fa547bacf2278f4.jpg" /><br /></p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left">You can go to detail page to find your tracking number and check shipping status by express tracking site.</p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><img alt="" align="middle" src="/attachments/2012/06/13391744329100865f4adfc202.jpg" /></p><p><span style="color:#ff0000;">Note: Please check your item''s quantity inside the parcel before you sign, we are not responsible for the loss once you sign the consignment note. </span> </p><p>If you find any missing items, please write down the product detail and missing quantity on your consignment note and give back to the courier. </p><p>Then email to <a href="mailto:taobao4us@hotmail.com">taobao4us@hotmail.com</a> the photo of the parcel with the weight show together.</p><p>We will verify with our shipping agent in China and will get back to you after we get reply.</p><p>&nbsp; </p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left">4. Click &quot;Confirm&quot; and leave your testimonial when you receive your order.</p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><img alt="" align="middle" src="/attachments/2012/06/13391748838aa27b0c480aa8b8.jpg" /><br /></p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><img alt="" align="middle" src="/attachments/2012/06/133917494911e3c43341032138.jpg" /><br /></p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left">Your delivered order will be shown as &quot;Finished&quot;.</p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><img alt="" align="middle" src="/attachments/2012/06/1339175128ad2aef1c77390ea5.jpg" /><br /></p><p>There are also some other status below maybe happened:</p><p><span style="color:#ff6666;">Cancelling</span>: Order status will be &quot;Cancelling&quot; when you click cancel before checkout .</p><p>Cancelled: Order status will be &quot;Cancelled&quot; when your cancel request is approved.</p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"> </p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left">&nbsp;</p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left">&nbsp;</p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><span style="font-size:32px;color:#666666;">Charge Policy</span></p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;">Taobao4US'' total fee = First payment + Second payment</span></p><p align="left"><strong>First payment:&nbsp; </strong>Items'' fee + China domestic shipping fee</p><p align="left"><strong>Second payment: </strong>International shipping fee + Service fee + Customs fee</p><p align="left">Taobao4US'' payment methods : PayPal</p><p align="left"><br /></p><p align="left"><strong><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;">1.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Service fee:</span></strong></p><p align="left">Taobao4US'' service fee = (Items fee + domestic shipping fee) X <span style="font-size:24px;"><span style="color:#ff0000;">6</span><strong><span style="color:#ff0000;">%</span></strong></span></p><p align="left">SVIP member will enjoy service fee as low as <span style="font-size:24px;color:#ff0000;">5%</span>.</p><p align="left">The minimum service charge is 5.0 USD per parcel. </p><p align="left">For example:<br />If the items costs 100USD and domestic shipping is 6USD, Taobao4US will charge you 6.36 USD service fee.<br />(100+6)×0.06 = 6.36USD<br /><br />If the items costs 10USD, and domestic shipping is 3.6USD, Taobao4US will charge you 5USD.<br />(10+3.6)×0.06 =&nbsp; 0.816USD ＜5USD<br /><br />Note:Taobao4US storage time limit is 180 days, and during this time, your order status is &quot;Arrived&quot;; we won''t help you to store if the date is more than 180 days and then your order status will change to &quot;Invalid&quot;. &quot;Invalid&quot; means that your''ve given up your items and we will handle them in our way. </p><p align="left"><br /></p><p align="left"><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;">2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>Items fee:</strong></span> </p><p align="left">The item price is as shown on the shopping site you browsing. </p><p align="left"><br /></p><p align="left"><strong><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;">3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Domestic shipping fee: </span></strong></p><p align="left">Most domestic delivery companies charge 12 to 30 CNY per kilogram. The fee differs according to the courier, parcel weight and the distance between seller and buyer''s locations. </p><p align="left">For the items from same seller, if the total weight from this seller is below 1kg, we will charge you one time. If above 1kg, you need to pay the balance.</p><p align="left"><br /></p><p align="left"><strong><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;">4.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; International delivery fee: </span></strong></p><p align="left">Taobao4US provide various delivery methods, such as: EMS, Airmail for small packages, Air Parcel, SAL Parcel, Domestic forwarding.&nbsp; </p><p align="left"><br /></p><p align="left"><strong>5.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Customs fee: </strong></p><p align="left">We suggest that before shipping, Taobao4US customers take the initiative to find out policies of their local customs. In countries with high rate of customs clearance, there is no need to pay any fees. However, in countries with low rate of customs clearance such as Argentina, customers may be required to pay tariffs. </p><p align="left">Note: Chinese customs fee is <span>(Items fee + domestic shipping fee)*1%</span>. </p><p align="left"><br /></p><p align="left"><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;">When to pay the service fee?</span></span></p><p align="left">You will be asked to pay service charge together with the international shipping fee for your parcel. After you get the weight of your parcel and have selected the international shipping method, Taobao4US will automatically calculate the service fee for you. At that point, you will need to pay the shipping costs and service fee, and Taobao4US will ship your parcel.<br /><br /></p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left">&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', '1', '', '1'),
(15, 1338546683, 1362174906, 4, 'Measurement Help', '<strong><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;">How to get the right clothes size?</span></strong> <p align="left">Do you feel frustrated or annoyed if you buy the wrong size of clothes online? Because the body shapes of people are different; different brand of clothes also have different size standard. So some people sometimes will worry about the clothes size they choose if correct or wonder how to find the correct clothes size. Then how do we avoid choosing the wrong size that does not fit us perfectly? Here are some advices to figure out the correct size of clothes and make your online shopping process a great fun. </p><p align="left"><br /></p><p align="left"><strong><span style="font-family:''Arial Black'';font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;">Measure yourself by using a flexible measuring tape</span></strong></p><p align="left">It is very useful to have a plastic measuring tape in hand when shopping online. You must know your clear dimension of bust/chest, waist, and hips and so on. So measure yourself first. <strong>Please do not pull the tape tightly when measuring. And be aware that the tape remains parallel to the floor. </strong></p><p align="left"><strong>A: Shoulder Width</strong><br />Stand erect and relaxed, measure across upper back from end of one shoulder bone (top of arm) to the other end of shoulder bone (top of arm). </p><p align="left"><strong>B: Bust/chest</strong><br />Stand erect and relaxed, then measure your bust/chest around the fullest part of your bust/chest line with the tape passing under the arms in a circle. (If you are female, it is important to wear a bra to be accurate.) </p><p align="left"><strong>C: Waist</strong><br />Stand relaxed and breathe out, measure around your natural waistline which is the narrowest part near your belly button. </p><p align="left"><strong>D: Hips</strong><br />Stand still with your feet normally apart and put the tape around the fullest part of your hips in one circle. </p><p align="left"><strong>E: Arm Length</strong><br />Put your one arm at the side, place one end of the tape at the nape of the neck and measure to the shoulder and down the arm to the wrist. </p><p align="left">After taking the measurements correctly, you have to pay attention to one more thing. You must know clothes you choose are<strong> tight or loose, larger or smaller than usual.</strong> You may need to <strong>float the size up and down</strong> according to the pattern, material or item description shown online. And also it is necessary to have a look at other buyers'' comments and suggestions. <strong>(Please be aware that Chinese size is a little smaller than international size.)</strong> </p><p align="left">If you are still not very sure about the clothes size, <strong>please kindly write down your body sizes including your body height, weight, bust/chest, hips etc., and then ask our customer service for help.</strong> We will help you to coordinate and communicate with online sellers. The sellers will give some advices, and then you can decide by yourself. </p>', '1', '', 'measurement-help'),
(16, 1338546718, 1362172982, 4, 'Taobao in English', '<p align="left"><span style="font-family:Arial Black;font-size:18px;color:#cc0000;"><strong>How to&nbsp;buy from taobao.com&nbsp; in English</strong></span> </p><p align="left">Dear Taobao4US Clients, </p><p align="left">To make sure your shopping from China is&nbsp;easy and convenient,&nbsp;Taobao4US will introduce how to buy from Taobao in English with automatic translation web browser Google Chrome. </p><p align="left"><strong>Taobao4US strongly recommend you to use the Google Chrome web browser to browse Chinese websites.</strong> </p><p align="left">1. When you are viewing Chinese shopping online websites such as Taobao, we strongly recommend you to use Google Chrome web browser. By using Chrome automatic translation, it will become so easy for you to translate the content into English. <br /></p><p align="left">2. When you have a choice, you can copy the URL into&nbsp;Taobao4US and make a order. We will&nbsp;process your order within 6 hours. Every step is easy and fast, and&nbsp;the service charge and shipping&nbsp;fee&nbsp;are competitive.&nbsp;</p><p align="left"></p><p align="left">You can get Chrome from: <u>https://www.google.com/chrome</u></p><br />', '1', '', 'taobao-in-english'),
(17, 1338546750, 1362259406, 5, 'Place Order', '<p align="left"><strong>1. Please first register on&nbsp;taobao4us.com and login, if you choose products from Taobao, please copy product link in “Quick Order” text box.</strong></p><p align="left"><strong><img alt="" align="middle" src="http://www.taobaoenglishagent.com/attachments/2012/06/1339169576217509da2d975607.jpg" /><br /></strong></p><p align="left"><strong>You will find product detail page, select size, color, and input quantity.&nbsp;</strong><span style="color:#ff00;">Note: The selected color will be grey if&nbsp;it is out of stock.</span></p><p align="left"><strong><img alt="" align="middle" src="http://www.taobaoenglishagent.com/attachments/2012/06/1339170368a9755593eecf69a0.jpg" width="800" /><br /></strong></p><p align="left"><strong>Click&nbsp;&quot;Buy Now&quot; to go to shopping cart page, or&nbsp;click &quot;Add to cart&quot;&nbsp;to continue shopping.</strong></p><p align="left"><strong><br /></strong></p><p align="left"></p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><strong>2.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Go to your shopping cart page, you can change quantity in your shopping cart and click &quot;save&quot; to apply.&nbsp;</strong></p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><strong><img alt="" align="middle" src="http://www.taobaoenglishagent.com/attachments/2012/06/13391708996997aefc1923a201.jpg" width="800" /><br /></strong></p><p style="font-weight: bold;" align="left"><strong>Click&nbsp;&quot;Generate Order&quot; to generate a new purchase order. You will be lead to purchase order page.</strong></p><div><strong><br /></strong></div>', '1', '', 'place-order');
